original_text: The heaven, even the heavens, are the Lord's: but the earth hath he given to the children of men.
korean_text: 하늘은 여호와의 하늘이라도 땅은 사람에게 주셨도다

sentences.original_text: The heaven, even the heavens, are the Lord's
sentences.korean_translation: 하늘, 그 모든 하늘은 주의 것이다

sentences.original_text: but the earth has he given to the children of men
